CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1953, pg. 2, reads: "At Southwest PTA Conference - The Southwestern Pennsylvania Conference of Parent Teacher Association was held at the William Penn Hotel last Saturday. Shown during the sessions are, left photo: Mrs. Kenneth Scott, Mrs. Dorothy Harper, Mrs. Maud Cooley, Mrs. Lillian Vaughn and Mrs. Charleszetta Primas...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right; Mrs. Kenneth Scott, Dorothy Harper, Maud Cooley, Lillian Vaughn and Charleszetta Primas, standing in William Penn Hotel for PTA conference
